Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经也是个英雄 该死的\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}SALLY: I was a hero, goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,此举明显是向西贡政府发出信号…\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}MAN [ON TV]:an act clearly meant to send a signal to the government in Saigon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(越战升级)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力和镇压不是和平之道\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}... that violence and oppression is not the way to peace.
