Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.91,1:00:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,埋葬于雨中\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Buried in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.17,1:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被谋杀\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Murdered.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.07,1:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的下场吗?\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is that what happens to us?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.67,1:00:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间交朋友?\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}No time for friends?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.14,1:00:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们的敌人留下玫瑰\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Only our enemies leave roses.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.61,1:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力的人生以暴力终结\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Violent lives ending violently.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.49,1:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,布雷克早就明白 人类的天性是野蛮的\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Blake understood. Humans are savage in nature.
