Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.98,1:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我听过一个笑话\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}I heard joke once.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.84,1:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一个男人去看医生 说他很沮丧\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Man goes to doctor, says he's depressed.
