Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.09,1:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"伟大的小丑帕格里亚齐来了 去看他的表演吧\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}"The great clown Pagliacci is in town. Go see him.
