Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.59,2:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.10,2:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.44,2:17:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来 都上去\N{\fs40\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, let's move it, people.
